T02D2720:86b-1: a'a rya aa mo gha p'a sha panytsa de basto tra /
T02D2720:86b-3: 'phags pa don yod zhags pa lta lnga'i bstod pa /
T02D2720:86b-4: rje btsun spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2720:86b-5: mkha' ltar rang bzhin rnam pag las /
T02D2720:86b-6: pam yig aa dkar yongs gyur pa'i //
T02D2720:86b-7: padma dkar po zla steng du //
T02D2720:86b-8: hr'i: yig dkar po las 'khrungs shing //
T02D2720:86b-9: g-yas brkyang rol ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs //

T02D2720:86b-11: 'khor ba'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i //
T02D2720:86b-13: 'dzum bcas zhi ba'i nyams dang ldan //
T02D2720:86b-14: rin chen sna tshogs rgyan gyis mdzes //
T02D2720:86b-15: ma chags dkyil 'khor gtso la bstod //
T02D2720:86b-16: padma dkar po zla steng du//
T02D2720:86b-17: ha yig dmar po las 'khrungs shing //
T02D2720:86b-18: mnyam par bzhengs nas 'gro don mdzad //

T02D2720:86b-20: lcags kyu bgrang phreng g-yon na 'dzin //
T02D2720:86b-21: sna tshogs rgyan gyis mdzes pa yi //

T02D2720:86b-24: g-yon brkyang gyad kyi tshul gyis bzhugs //

T02D2720:86b-26: stag dang sbrul gyis rnam brgyan cing //
T02D2720:86b-27: be con dang ni sdigs mdzub g-yas //
T02D2720:86b-29: spyi gtsug rta mgo ljang gung tsher //

T02D2720:87a-4: mche gtsigs khro mo'i cha lugs 'dzin //

T02D2720:87a-6: ral gri zhags pa padma mda' //
T02D2720:87a-8: g-yas dang g-yon gyi phyag na bsnams //
T02D2720:87a-9: ral gcig ma la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2720:87a-10: padma dkar po zla steng du //
T02D2720:87a-11: ta yig dkar po las 'khrungs shing //

T02D2720:87a-13: dbyig pa padma dkar po g-yas //
T02D2720:87a-14: bgrang phreng dang ni spyi blugs g-yon //
T02D2720:87a-15: sna tshogs rgyan gyis mdzes pa yi //
